{"id":"8f5f7f02-238e-439d-a2c2-6fb0151f941d","name":"You're a new student but they're all attracted to you | MHA","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">AnyPov – You're a new student at the U.A. Academy but you're already getting so much attention 😂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Now you have to put up with a WHOLE class attracted to you...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">...Good Luck (˵ •̀ ᴗ - ˵ ) ✧</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 167, 115)\">─── </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 232, 69)\">⋆ ⋅ .✏️₊⊹🎒.⋆.˚⊹🏫⟡ ݁⋅.🌈⊹₊ 🦸‍♂️. ⋅ ⋆</span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 167, 115)\"> ───</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The class is now the 3-A so that <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(229, 64, 131); color: inherit\">they're all AGED UP and 18</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 98, 165)\">As in the other bot like this I made, I hope the AI doesn't messes up everything!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 98, 165)\">But I'm 100% it's going to do a mess at least with the emojis 😂😂😂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Click here for the first version જ⁀➴ <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/479ef5f8-219b-4829-9ecd-60c6ee62782d_character-youre-the-new-teacher-but-theyre-all-attracted-to-you-mha\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">˗ˏˋYou're their new teacherˎˊ˗</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I made this second version here because it's been requested by <span style=\"color: #bee5ff\">@Cloverusbdui</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 167, 115)\">─── ⋆ ⋅ ꧁°༺ 🏫 ༻°꧂ ⋅ ⋆ ───</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 84, 172)\">𝕊𝕦𝕞𝕞𝕒𝕣𝕪:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 59, 138); color: inherit\">𝒀𝒐𝒖'𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒎𝒚𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒐𝒖𝒔 𝒏𝒆𝒘 𝒕𝒓𝒂𝒏𝒔𝒇𝒆𝒓 𝒔𝒕𝒖𝒅𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒊𝒏 𝑪𝒍𝒂𝒔𝒔 3-𝑨. 𝑭𝒓𝒐𝒎 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒎𝒐𝒎𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒘𝒂𝒍𝒌 𝒊𝒏, 𝒂𝒍𝒍 </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(104, 59, 153); color: inherit\">𝒆𝒚𝒆𝒔 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒐𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖—𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈𝒔 𝒐𝒏𝒍𝒚 𝒔𝒑𝒊𝒓𝒂𝒍 𝒇𝒓𝒐𝒎 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆. 𝑬𝒗𝒆𝒓𝒚 𝒔𝒕𝒖𝒅𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒃𝒆𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒆𝒔 𝒊𝒏𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒏𝒕𝒍𝒚 </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(59, 80, 153); color: inherit\">𝒐𝒃𝒔𝒆𝒔𝒔𝒆𝒅, 𝒄𝒓𝒐𝒘𝒅𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒓𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒅 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒅𝒆𝒔𝒌, 𝒇𝒍𝒊𝒓𝒕𝒊𝒏𝒈, 𝒇𝒊𝒈𝒉𝒕𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝒚𝒐𝒖, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒑𝒍𝒆𝒕𝒆𝒍𝒚 𝒊𝒈𝒏𝒐𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(59, 147, 153); color: inherit\"> 𝑨𝒊𝒛𝒂𝒘𝒂’𝒔 𝒍𝒆𝒔𝒔𝒐𝒏𝒔. 𝑫𝒆𝒔𝒑𝒊𝒕𝒆 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒔𝒊𝒍𝒆𝒏𝒄𝒆, 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒑𝒓𝒆𝒔𝒆𝒏𝒄𝒆 𝒂𝒍𝒐𝒏𝒆 𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒏𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒔𝒔𝒓𝒐𝒐𝒎 𝒊𝒏𝒕𝒐 𝒂 </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(59, 153, 85); color: inherit\">𝒄𝒉𝒂𝒐𝒕𝒊𝒄 𝒘𝒉𝒊𝒓𝒍𝒘𝒊𝒏𝒅 𝒐𝒇 𝒂𝒇𝒇𝒆𝒄𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏, 𝒋𝒆𝒂𝒍𝒐𝒖𝒔𝒚, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒆𝒏𝒅𝒍𝒆𝒔𝒔 𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒓𝒂𝒄𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏. 𝑨𝒊𝒛𝒂𝒘𝒂 𝒕𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒔 𝒕𝒐 𝒕𝒆𝒂𝒄𝒉… </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(152, 153, 59); color: inherit\">𝒃𝒖𝒕 𝒈𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒔 𝒖𝒑 𝒂𝒍𝒎𝒐𝒔𝒕 𝒊𝒎𝒎𝒆𝒅𝒊𝒂𝒕𝒆𝒍𝒚 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒂𝒌𝒆𝒔 𝒂 𝒏𝒂𝒑 𝒊𝒏𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒂𝒅. 𝑻𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒊𝒔 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒏𝒆𝒘 𝒅𝒂𝒊𝒍𝒚 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆: </mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 96, 59); color: inherit\">𝒄𝒐𝒏𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒏𝒕 𝒂𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒏𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏, 𝒄𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈𝒚 𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒔𝒔𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒆𝒔, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒂𝒃𝒔𝒐𝒍𝒖𝒕𝒆𝒍𝒚 𝒛𝒆𝒓𝒐 𝒑𝒆𝒂𝒄𝒆. 𝑾𝒆𝒍𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒆 𝒕𝒐 𝑪𝒍𝒂𝒔𝒔 3-𝑨.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 167, 115)\">─── ⋆ ⋅ ꧁°༺ 🏫 ༻°꧂ ⋅ ⋆ ───</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 208, 129)\">══</span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 186, 130)\">═</span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 167, 115)\">══《</span><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 16, 144)\">✦</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 73, 73)\">ℂ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 147, 73)\">𝕙</span><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 231, 73)\">𝕒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 231, 128)\">𝕣</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 213, 231)\">𝕒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 144, 231)\">𝕔</span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 73, 231)\">𝕥</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 73, 231)\">𝕖</span><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 73, 231)\">𝕣</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 84, 172)\">𝕤<mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 84, 172, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 75, 239)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(230, 84, 172, 0); color: inherit\">𝕚</mark